## French Bikini Wax

Bikini waxing is a process of removing unwanted hair from the genital area. It often involves the removal of all visible pubic hair, as well as hair from the inner thighs and buttocks (depending on the desired outcome). The bikini wax should only be done when the skin is clean and dry, and it is important to prepare your skin before waxing to reduce irritation and discomfort. Before undergoing any kind of bikini waxing, it is best to consult with a doctor or dermatologist as they can advise you on what type of procedure would be right for you.

Provides a basic level of grooming: A basic bikini wax is a quick and easy way to tidy up the bikini area, providing a basic level of grooming. It is a good option for those who want to remove excess hair around the bikini line but don't want to go for full hair removal.

Cost-effective: Basic bikini waxing is generally less expensive than other types of bikini waxing. This makes it a great option for those who want to maintain their bikini line without breaking the bank.

Longer-lasting results: One advantage of French bikini waxing is that it tends to provide longer-lasting results than other hair removal methods. This is because the wax removes hair from the root, which means that it takes longer for hair to grow back than if it were simply shaved off at the surface level.

More thorough hair removal: Another advantage of French bikini waxing is that it tends to be a more thorough method of hair removal than shaving or trimming. This is because the wax can remove even very short hairs, which may be difficult to capture with a razor or scissors. Additionally, since the wax adheres to the hair and removes it from the root, it can help to prevent ingrown hairs and leave the skin feeling smoother.

Smooth and clean feeling: One of the main advantages of getting a Hollywood wax is that it provides a smooth and clean feeling in the pubic area. Unlike shaving or other hair removal methods, which can leave stubble or cause irritation, a Hollywood wax removes all the hair from the bikini area, leaving the skin feeling soft and smooth.

Provides a cleaner look: With an extended bikini wax, you can achieve a cleaner look than with a basic bikini wax. This can be particularly useful if you prefer to wear high-cut swimsuits or underwear.

Less discomfort: While an extended bikini wax removes more hair than a basic bikini wax, it can be less painful than a French or Brazilian bikini wax because it doesn't involve removing as much hair.

Clean and polished look: The high bikini wax is perfect for those who prefer a clean and polished look around the bikini area. It provides a neat and tidy appearance without removing all of the hair.

Great for thong wearers: If you love wearing thongs, a high bikini wax is a must-have. It removes all of the hair that would be visible in a thong, leaving you free to wear whatever you like.

